{"tid":1872030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【整合】「武肺鍋」一家18口最新情況！","createTime":"2020-02-09T23:33:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T11:43:13.000Z","uid":202464,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"e5a68278c0b63864a374489eee50917af783cd7c","tid":1872030,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T23:33:19.000Z","msg":"2020年1月26日，年初二：<br />\n<br />\n「武漢鍋」一家18口去觀塘永興工業大廈4樓C4室「Lento Party Room」打邊爐同BBQ<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1月30日，年初六：<br />\n灣仔駱克道鴻福大廈一名24 歲男子發燒加咳嗽，去私家醫生求診<br />\n<br />\n2 月 4 日，正月十一：<br />\n再向另一名私家醫生求診<br />\n<br />\n2 月 6 日，正月十三：<br />\n到聖保祿醫院門診部求醫<br />\n<br />\n2 月 8 日，正月十五：<br />\n到律敦治醫院急症室求醫，確診武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n************<br />\n<br />\n已經中招親友：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">灣仔駱克道356-362號鴻福大廈：</span><br />\n68歲父親、57歲母親、<br />\n91歲外婆（患癌，曾去東區醫院普通病房留醫8日）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">銅鑼灣禮頓道42-56號禮智大廈：</span><br />\n51歲三姨、25歲表姐、22歲表弟、<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">灣仔駱克道89號中滙大廈：</span><br />\n50歲四姨、23歲表弟，<br />\n<br />\n**************<br />\n<br />\n另外 10 名有份食「武肺鍋」既親戚，有 2 人出現病徵，未證實是否感染武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n另有2名支那親戚已經返廣東，情況不詳。"},{"pid":"db253e4614ecf0ec5c81b0fd6cd51fc0d0cdf59b","tid":1872030,"uid":277186,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T23:36:33.000Z","msg":"港島區gg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過不嬲多大陸人"},{"pid":"8a8eb6a6e83a55f28d193d3704d45fa090e8af74","tid":1872030,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db253e4614ecf0ec5c81b0fd6cd51fc0d0cdf59b","tid":1872030,"uid":277186,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T23:36:33.000Z","msg":"港島區gg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過不嬲多大陸人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T23:38:10.000Z","msg":"全部灣仔區。"},{"pid":"8f572104b2bc49f31925eafe821c83f6cfcccaff","tid":1872030,"uid":175870,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T23:42:10.000Z","msg":"//年初二（1月26日）在觀塘Lento Party Room一同吃火鍋的19人家族，至少9人確診感染可致命的武漢肺炎，包括一名91歲婆婆。消息指，婆婆最初因發燒，入住東區醫院急症內科E4病房7日，幸好來接她出院的孫兒向醫護透露，婆婆曾與其中一名初步確診者一同吃火鍋，才令醫護改變決定，不讓婆婆出院「播毒」。不過婆婆被送入隔離病房前，曾在E4病房近距離接觸至少20名護士，這些護士更不獲隔離和接受病毒測試。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果醬//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望護士冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39126208d4dd2fb7746e8f1f2a1a31d1f165059f","tid":1872030,"uid":128271,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T23:43:22.000Z","msg":"武漢鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次火鍋店可以用呢個名"},{"pid":"8dbacc65d8c16a8f33d1d24daf685680473265dc","tid":1872030,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T23:44:35.000Z","msg":"24歲攬炒藍絲廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有兩件支那"},{"pid":"0914994c668cecf3930185f048d0d621acdb03d4","tid":1872030,"uid":149342,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T23:45:46.000Z","msg":"希望同大厦party緊嘅都中"},{"pid":"aeb771ceb58fbe3ada1454baaf36cbd771563d23","tid":1872030,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dbacc65d8c16a8f33d1d24daf685680473265dc","tid":1872030,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T23:44:35.000Z","msg":"24歲攬炒藍絲廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有兩件支那"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T23:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051e558129fd3cb7067dcbf91486e4594a7c0f39","tid":1872030,"uid":203619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T23:46:38.000Z","msg":"死清光<img sr